Colonel John Farter, an American officer who has spent seven years in a North Vietnamese POW camp, has just returned to discover his hometown full of zombies. And his only weapon against them is his ass.

Join Farter as he join his old friend Banana Max and, together, free the town from The Evil Unicorn and his army of zombies!

In Farts VS Zombies you have to kill zombies with farts, you draw with the finger the path of the farts and direct them to their faces. Protect the Japanese schoolgirls from the attack of the zombies for as long as possible!

